cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

This paper is primarily focused on robotic learning, specifically in the context of self-supervised goal-conditioned reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques such as reinforcement learning and proposes a conditional goal-setting model, which suggests that it could also fit into the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper uses raw image observations, indicating that it could also belong to the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of goal setting in a diverse environment, which suggests that it could also fit into the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
